Package org.cibseven.bpm.engine.impl.form.engine

Class HtmlFormEngine

java.lang.Object
org.cibseven.bpm.engine.impl.form.engine.HtmlFormEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
FormEngine
public class HtmlFormEngine extends Object implements FormEngine

A simple FormEngine implementaiton which renders forms as HTML such that they can be used as embedded forms inside camunda Tasklist.

Author:
Daniel Meyer
